{"word":"ἰβυκτήρ","slug":"ἰβυκτήρ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n49799\" key=\"i)bukth/r\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἰβυκτήρ</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ῆρος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, in Cretan, <sense id=\"n49799.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">one who begins a war-song</tr_>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl> (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-βηκ-</foreign> cod.). <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἰβύκχα·</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σεμνότης, ἢ σωρὸς κρεῶν</foreign>, Id. (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-ύηχ-</foreign> cod.). <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἶβυξ</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">υκος</itype>,= <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἶβις</foreign>, Id. <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἴβυς</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">υος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>,= <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εὐφημία, στιγμή</foreign>, Id. <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἰβύω</orth>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">shout: strike</tr_>, Id.; cf. <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἰβῶν·</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εὐφημῶν, στάζων</foreign>, Id. <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἴγα</orth>, in Cretan,= <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σίγα</foreign>, Id. <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἴγγι</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τινί</foreign>: <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπιθυμίᾳ τινὶ ἑλκομένη</foreign>, Id. (leg. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἴυγγι</foreign>). <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἴγγια·</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἷς</foreign> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Cypr.</author> </bibl>), Id. <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἴγδην</orth> and <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἴγνην·</orth> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄρσην</foreign>, Id.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}